16:04.347 --> 16:07.387
In the cleft.
Stay away from the cleft.

16:11.907 --> 16:15.667
You see what I'm saying?
Some people aren't even bothering
with the strawberries.

16:15.707 --> 16:17.987
OK, we need to get out of here.
I know, but how? I dunno.

16:18.027 --> 16:20.227
Maybe sneak out? What? Sneak out?

16:20.267 --> 16:23.867
I think people might notice
if the cream covered
human statue tries to sneak out.

16:23.907 --> 16:26.787
Copier! Circulate.
Yeah, sorry. I am.

16:28.427 --> 16:30.427
So many options.

16:34.147 --> 16:35.747
How's it going? Rubbish.

16:35.787 --> 16:37.827
It's like being at work,
but in a rented toga.

16:37.867 --> 16:39.947
It's nearly ten. This is dog shit.

16:39.987 --> 16:42.867
We can't stay here all night.
We can't leave. She'll fire us.

16:42.907 --> 16:46.387
