I thought you liked me. I do.
You just said you didn't.

17:01.947 --> 17:03.867
It's a phrase.
Not for when you like someone.

17:03.907 --> 17:06.666
Hey! I think you're great, Aurelius.

17:06.707 --> 17:11.146
So, why did you just say -
Now, help us get out of here
and you can meet the hot girls.

17:11.987 --> 17:15.587
