the atmosphere will be awful.

17:43.307 --> 17:45.627
Cos I was thinking
you could diddle the water clock

17:45.667 --> 17:48.147
and we could bring midnight
forward an hour.

17:48.187 --> 17:51.667
Yeah. Let's do that.

18:07.107 --> 18:09.027
Right, well...

18:09.067 --> 18:11.587
Thanks for the rub down
and the scroll and that.

18:11.627 --> 18:15.867
Well, may Sibyli bless you
on your holy journey.

18:15.907 --> 18:19.627
May...he...bless you -
Is it a he or she?

18:19.667 --> 18:21.347
Have you read the scroll?

18:21.387 --> 18:23.627
Hmmm. Hmmm? Hmmm?

18:23.667 --> 18:25.467
It's a she, ain't it? Mm-hm.

18:25.507 --> 18:27.667
Cos of the boobs.

18:27.707 --> 18:32.147
