pop on to the back of the cart there
with the other trainees.

18:32.187 --> 18:35.027
Oh, right.
Are we gonna get dropped off, then?

18:35.067 --> 18:36.827
I were just gonna walk it.

18:36.867 --> 18:38.787
Precious. No, no, no.

18:38.827 --> 18:40.827
Up you pop.

18:45.467 --> 18:47.987
It's time! Everybody, let's go!

18:48.027 --> 18:51.267
10... Is it midnight already?

18:51.307 --> 18:53.987
7...6...5...

18:56.427 --> 18:59.147
Sorry, which way are we going?
Cos I live back that way.

18:59.187 --> 19:03.107
We're heading to the docks.
It'll only take a couple of hours.

19:03.147 --> 19:07.587
Right, don't mean to be
