That sounds... Is it hot, Cyprus?

19:23.947 --> 19:27.347
Cyprus? Oh, very hot. Yes. Very hot.

19:27.387 --> 19:29.147
Like, nice hot? Not too hot, hot?

19:29.187 --> 19:31.307
