20:14.947 --> 20:17.227
Salve, Marcus. Landlord.

20:17.267 --> 20:19.787
Ready for the frenzy?
Yeah, they've not hit the gong yet?

20:19.827 --> 20:21.867
No, any moment now. Brace yourselves.

20:21.907 --> 20:24.747
Listen. Have you seen Cynthia?
Haven't seen bugger all, mate.

20:24.787 --> 20:29.307
I had these mushrooms
that have given me bat-shit mental
hallucinations and stomach cramps.

20:29.347 --> 20:31.147
Do you want some? No, thanks. I will.

20:31.187 --> 20:33.867
Ah, good lad. Covered in cream, then?

20:33.907 --> 20:36.227
Yep. Classic.

20:36.267 --> 20:40.187
Are there any other doughnut
sellers, Landlord? In the Forum?

20:40.227 --> 20:42.187
Landlord?

20:42.227 --> 20:43.907
Doughnut sellers?

20:43.947 --> 20:45.587
Shitloads, mate.

20:45.627 --> 20:48.987
But I've been having these quadruple
visions, or something, so who knows?

20:49.027 --> 20:51.147
Good luck with that.

20:51.187 --> 20:53.627
Thanks for the mushrooms.
Yeah, no problem.

21:01.627 --> 21:03.907
Doughnuts!

21:03.947 --> 21:06.947
Hey, Cynthia! Oh, wow. You found us!

21:06.987 --> 21:10.707
Yeah, hi. Sorry. We got a bit lost -
And covered in cream.
I got covered in cream, yes.

21:10.747 --> 21:13.147
Lovely to meet you, I'm Aurelius.
All set for the gong?

21:13.187 --> 21:16.907
Oh, it's my favourite instrument.
I'm Aurelius. All right, mate.
Back off. What?

21:16.947 --> 21:19.587
Oh, this is so exciting!
